How do I make a quick buck?.answer:
Making a quick buck is a rather difficult task. Nevertheless, you can attempt the following methods:

1. Sell items that are no longer needed, such as clothing, books, and secondhand items that can be resold;

2. Join a group of people and rent out your spare rooms to make some extra money;

3. Carry out short-term part-time jobs such as making handwritten documents, packing boxes, and ferrying goods.
